 the PDF of the produced maps. An extension of ALMA's capabilities would\nallow us to recover the high-column density tail of the PDF but we found no way\nto measure the intermediate and low column density part of the underlying cloud\nPDF in interferometric observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Mar 2016 17:35:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 21 Mar 2016 16:20:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 14 Apr 2016 09:22:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-25"}
