roduce known results on the scaling of mid-gap\nMajorana states and demonstrate the origin of its log-normal distribution, ii)\nidentify contrasting behavior of disorder-dependent GS parity switches for the\ncases of even versus odd number of lattice sites, and iii) chart out the GS\nparity configuration and associated parity switch points as a function of\ndisorder strength.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Mar 2016 19:48:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-14"}
