uments. We prove this interesting\nfeature at all orders at the level of the Schr\\\"odinger equation for general\npotentials in the considered class.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Mar 2016 11:11:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-25"}
