 density at finite temperature, which\nis studied analytically (at low temperature), as well as numerically for the\nsu$(1|1)$ elliptic chain.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Mar 2016 15:44:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-08"}
